## ISML → React Mapping

| ISML Pattern | React 19 Equivalent |
|--------------|---------------------|
| `<isif>` | Conditional rendering `{condition && <Component />}` |
| `<isloop>` | `.map()` with key prop |
| `<isinclude>` | Component import |
| Bootstrap class | Tailwind equivalent |

## jQuery → React Mapping

| jQuery Pattern | React 19 Equivalent |
|----------------|---------------------|
| `$.ajax()` | Server Action or fetch in loader |
| `$(el).on('click')` | `onClick` handler |
| `$(el).addClass()` | State-driven className |

